    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-5">This saves the state of your bundle locally on your machine, which can help to recover from errors. The saves are temporary though! If you want a long-term save, just press <strong>Create Bundle</strong> and save a full copy. Remember, you can always pick up from where you left off by clicking <strong>Edit an existing bundle</strong>.</p>
